Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like a cruel angel{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.14,0:00:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Become a legend, young boy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When a blue wind{\i0}\N{\i1}Knocks on the door to your heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.77,0:00:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just gaze back at me{\i0}\N{\i1}And smile oh so gently{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.70,0:00:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So eager for something{\i0}\N{\i1}You touch so softly{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.80,0:00:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those innocent eyes{\i0}\N{\i1}Know nothing of the fate that awaits{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.39,0:00:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But one day, you will realize{\i0}\N{\i1}That upon your back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have wings{\i0}\N{\i1}You can fly to the faraway future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The cruel angel's thesis{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, you'll take off through a window{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If your overflowing pathos{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.53,0:01:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leads you to betray your memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then embrace the heavens and shine bright{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Become legend, young boy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ready, Shinji?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Release final safeties!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.32,0:01:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Evangelion Unit 01, lift off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want you to just concentrate on walking.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.43,0:01:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take a step...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a step...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinji, pull it together!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry! Hurry, you need to get up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinji, stay calm!{\i0}\N{\i1}It only feels like your arm is being hurt!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where are its defensive systems?!\N-Signal inactive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Field not raised!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}Left forearm damaged!{\i0}\N-{\i1}Circuits severed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, break loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Fracture in frontal cranium!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The armor can't take much more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Skull damage! Severity unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Control neurons\Nare disconnecting in a cascade!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.77,0:03:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pilot readings lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know this ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Angels have returned.\NIt's all too sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Calamity never warns before striking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This might also be considered a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that all our previous\Ninvestments were worthwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That remains to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is not useful,\Nit is the same as wasted money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Information regarding the Angels\Nis spreading among the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We need a disinformation campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nerv's work must be carried out\Nboth properly and quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.73,0:04:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Those concerns are already\Nbeing addressed. Rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This morning at the Prime Minister's{\i0}\N{\i1}Office in Tokyo-2,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the government held a press--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}The government claims--{\i0}\N-{\i1}UN Forces Japan were deployed--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:05:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They went with Scenario B-22, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again, the facts get buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Public Affairs Office was ecstatic.\NThey say they finally feel useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bunch of optimists.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder.\NI think they're actually terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They have good reason to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's certainly true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, Ikari... can't you manage Nerv\Nand the Evas better?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,First there was Unit 00, and now\NUnit 01 needs repairs after its debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,These bills could bankrupt a country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you gave that toy to your own son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,People. Time. And money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You and your son seem to have\Nan insatiable appetite for resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is not your only job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Human Instrumentality Project.\NThat is your top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That project is the only glimmer of light\Nin this desperate situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity's only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In any event, there can be no\Npushing back the project's timetable
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,due to the Angels' arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your budget request will be considered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Council will take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari, there's no turning back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm well aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity's time is running out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, AC is humanity's greatest invention!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What a triumph of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:06:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji's regained consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's his condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No external injuries, but they say\Nhis memory's a little jumbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there psychological contamination?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They say there's no risk of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm not surprised.\NWe threw him into the deep end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder.\NHis cranial nerves took a lot of strain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"His heart," don't you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,NOTICE OF CONSTRUCTION\NGUIDED MUNITIONS SYS. BUILDING NO. 25
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Okay! Okay!\N-Keep it coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the Evas and this city are\Nfully operational, we might have a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You think we can win?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever the optimist, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, a bright outlook is essential\Nfor people to live their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.\NYour outlook is helpful sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Paging Dr. Ugai of{\i0}\N{\i1}Internal Medicine Department 1.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please contact Dr. Azuma{\i0}\N{\i1}of Surgery Department 1.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Medical conference regarding Incident B{\i0}\N{\i1}will take place as scheduled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All attendees, please gather{\i0}\N{\i1}in Conference Room 2.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure they should live separately?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,For the Ikaris, life without\Nthe other around is the norm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, living together\Nwould be strange for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He's living alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct. His quarters will be\Na room in Block Six nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is that acceptable?\N-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, I prefer being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all the same to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I'm going to have\NShinji live with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I got permission from the top brass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry,\NI won't mess around with some kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course you won't!{\i0}\N{\i1}Don't even suggest that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-She needs to learn to take a joke.\N{\i1}-You're always doing this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, then! We have to\Ncelebrate in style tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Celebrate what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The arrival of a new roommate, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're moving, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:10:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We never thought this city\Nwould actually become a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband wants me\Nand our children to evacuate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Evacuate, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They call this a fortress city,\Nbut we can't count on it to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I get chills just thinking about\Nwhat happened yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind,\Nwe're gonna make a quick detour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Someplace special.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of a desolate city, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Buildings are sprouting from the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the fortress city built to counter\Nand defeat the Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Tokyo-3. This is our city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And... it's the city that you protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I think your boxes of stuff\Nare already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I only moved here\Nrecently, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, thanks for having me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, this is your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's a little cluttered,\Nbut don't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She calls this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, could you put the groceries\Nin the fridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,snacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and beer is all she's got?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What does she do at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what's this other refrigerator for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, leave that one alone. I hate to bother\Nsomeone when they're sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what makes life worth living!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you hungry?\NIt's TV dinner food, but it's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I'm just not used to\Neating like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! We don't put up with\Nfussy eaters here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I... That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharing a meal with someone like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,let's do the next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot! Shoot! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we've now divided up\Nall our daily chores fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, this place is your home\Nstarting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So no standing on ceremony for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"Yes, ma'am" this and "Yes, ma'am" that!\NStop being so uptight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a boy, aren't you?!\NLet's hear some backbone and confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop into the tub\Nand wash all your cares away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The bath is life's washing machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.97,0:14:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a new hot-spring penguin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Pen-Pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Our other roomie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And... maybe you could cover up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I laid on{\i0}\N{\i1}the cheerfulness too thick.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He might see right through it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ms. Misato Katsuragi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess she's not a bad person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The bath is life's washing machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... I tend to remember{\i0}\N{\i1}all the bad things when I'm in the bath.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Father...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and Rei Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How was Rei, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand you visited her\Nat the hospital this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be back on her feet\Nin 20 days or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get Unit 00 up and running\Nand ready for reactivation by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be rough... on those children.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No one else can pilot the Evas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as they're alive,\Nthat's what they'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of how they feel about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.11,0:16:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,SHINJI'S ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,SCHOOL TRANSFER FORM:\NSHINJI IKARI
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}True, he was put through the wringer.{\i0}\N{\i1}I don't know if he'll do it again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Making sure he's operational{\i0}\N{\i1}is part of your job.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid.\NNot sure how I should approach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Whining already?\NYou were so dramatic about taking him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shove it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I said that,{\i0}\N{\i1}I just saw Shinji as a means to an end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm no different from Ritsuko.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He beat that Angel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So why aren't I happy about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Another ceiling I've never seen before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No surprise...{\i0}\N{\i1}Nothing about this city is familiar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I even here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Skull damage, severity unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Operational integrity compromised!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Synchrograph inverting!\NNeural pulse flow is reversing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut down circuits! Block the flow, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't! Shutdown signal rejected!\NIt's not getting through!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji's status?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero biometrics! Condition unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01 completely shut down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Abort operation!\NPilot rescue has top priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency plug eject, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't! System is\Ncompletely unresponsive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Eva has reactivated!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! It should be\Ncompletely non-operational!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-Has it gone...\N-...berserk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:18:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,An A.T. Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use!\NAs long as that field is up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...it can't touch the Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-Left arm restored!\N-Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01 has also raised an A.T. Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.43,0:19:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Angel's phase space\Nis being neutralized!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's {\i1}corroding{\i0} it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It tore through that A.T. Field\Nlike it was nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's self-destructing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.51,0:20:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Evas'...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.39,0:20:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Circuits connected.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}System back online.{\i0}\N{\i1}Graph readings at normal levels.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pilot's vitals confirmed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Expedite unit recovery.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pilot rescue has top priority!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji? I'm coming in for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,People will thank you\Nfor what you did today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.55,0:21:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.48,0:23:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.44,0:23:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With Shinji drifting through his new life,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there was little hope{\i0}\N{\i1}of him ever making friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.49,0:23:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the fact that he's the Eva's pilot{\i0}\N{\i1}makes him a celebrity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.46,0:23:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode! "The Silent Phone"!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}More fan service coming up next time, too!{\i0}
